                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">丹火印</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/5bef20ac953cae4a26b35ba84c55c406_7114752387451724106.png",
