                "title": "丹书立约"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">丹火印</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">灼灼</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/2c415dc76ad1e6437d2144d4c998f35b_299545217513501849.png",
                "id": "talent43720",
                "key": "凭此结契",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "凭此结契"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_6009973403637267129.png",
                "id": "talent84523",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">丹火印</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色进行重击时：</span>造成的伤害+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到2次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方开始行动前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的「普通攻击」将被视为「重击」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">灼灼</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色进行重击时：</span>少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">丹火印</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1222295744477533967.png",
